id="tabs-00-01" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-00-01-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt install nkf&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="usage">Usage&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>To convert any file to UTF-8 + LF:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>nkf -w -Lu --overwrite input_file
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>To convert C files in current directory to UTF-8 + LF:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>find . -iname &lt;span style="color:#ed9d13">&amp;#34;*.c&amp;#34;&lt;/span> -type f -print0 | xargs -0 nkf -w -LF --overwrite
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>Docs: ffmpeg</title><link>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/commands/ffmpeg/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/commands/ffmpeg/</guid><description>
