aria-controls="tabs-00-01" aria-selected="false">Ubuntu&lt;/a>
&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="tab-content" id="tabs-0-content">&lt;div class="tab-pane fade show active"
id="tabs-00-00" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-00-00-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo pacman -S ffmpeg&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;div class="tab-pane fade"
id="tabs-00-01" role="tabpanel" aria-labelled-by="tabs-00-01-tab">
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>sudo apt install ffmpeg&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/div>
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2 id="mp4-manipulation-with-ffmpeg">MP4 Manipulation with ffmpeg&lt;/h2>
&lt;table>
&lt;thead>
&lt;tr>
&lt;th style="text-align:left">Command&lt;/th>
&lt;th style="text-align:left">Description&lt;/th>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/thead>
&lt;tbody>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -crf 30 output.mp4&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Compression. The higher the crf value, the higher the compression ratio.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>ffmpeg -i input.mp4 -an output.mp4&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Mute audio.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table></description></item><item><title>Docs: platformio</title><link>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/commands/platformio/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/commands/platformio/</guid><description>
&lt;h2 id="install">Install&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>PlatformIO is written in Python. You can install following command:&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-sh" data-lang="sh">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>pip3 install platformio
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="basic-usage">Basic usage&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>You can use &lt;code>pio&lt;/code> instead of &lt;code>platformio&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;table>
&lt;thead>
&lt;tr>
&lt;th style="text-align:left">Command&lt;/th>
&lt;th style="text-align:left">Description&lt;/th>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/thead>
&lt;tbody>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio boards [Query]&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">You can see supported boards.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio init --board [ID]&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Initialize current directory.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio lib search [Query]&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Search library.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio lib show [Query]&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Show description of the library.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio lib install [ID or Name]&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Install library.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio lib uninstall [ID or Name]&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Uninstall library.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio run&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Build program.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio run --target upload&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Upload program.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio device monitor&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Show serial monitor.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;tr>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">&lt;code>pio device list&lt;/code>&lt;/td>
&lt;td style="text-align:left">Show list of device which is connected.&lt;/td>
&lt;/tr>
&lt;/tbody>
&lt;/table>
&lt;h2 id="directory-structure">Directory structure&lt;/h2>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>The directory structure looks like this.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#d0d0d0;background-color:#202020;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;">&lt;code class="language-text" data-lang="text">&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>./
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── .gitignore
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── .pio
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── libdeps
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── leonardo
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── ArduinoSTL_ID750
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ ├── .gitignore
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ ├── .library.json
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ ├── LICENSE
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ ├── README.md
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ ├── keywords.txt
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ ├── library.properties
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── src
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── .travis.yml
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── include
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── README
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── lib
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── README
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── platformio.ini
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>├── src
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>│ └── main.cpp
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span>└── test
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span style="display:flex;">&lt;span> └── README
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Your program have to be saved in the &lt;code>src/&lt;/code>.&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>.pio&lt;/code> sometimes has an useful example code.&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Docs: fwupd</title><link>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/commands/fwupd/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>http://forest0923.github.io/memo/en/docs/commands/fwupd/</guid><description>
